import { Link } from "react-router-dom"
import styles from './Menu.module.css'

const Menu = () => {
    return(
        <header>
            <nav className={styles.navegacao}>
                <Link className={styles.link} to={'/'}>
                    Home
                </Link>
                <Link className={styles.link} to={'/about'}>
                    About
                </Link>
            </nav>
        </header>
    )
}

export default Menu
